{"tid":954231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當年被嫌土！國中妹進化「兇到變天菜」　同學崩潰：我怎沒早發現","createTime":"2018-12-24T12:42:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T01:51:19.000Z","uid":212399,"like":43,"dislike":411,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"97864d6ff2d0244ad7ad762a3a7405f53009c30c","tid":954231,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:42:50.000Z","msg":"文／深海大花枝<br />\n人家都說女大十八變，用在日本推特這位「立花繭子」的身上就真的再適合也不過啦QQ。最近推特流行起了貼出小時候／現在照片對照圖的風潮，而今年才24歲的立花繭子，貼出來國中時的自己是這樣的......<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3757/3757562.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3757%2F3757562.jpg&h=4298d413&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然而經過了幾年，現在的她卻已經有了驚人的轉變......<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DuPXwog.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDuPXwog.jpg&h=19171cfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q613rWC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ613rWC.jpg&h=35bf47a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yx1i0gC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyx1i0gC.jpg&h=a2862eb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nsTUyBD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnsTUyBD.jpg&h=74bd27ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9VvorWE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9VvorWE.jpg&h=74f814f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BkAjKJk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBkAjKJk.jpg&h=a5891e79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u3grpJk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu3grpJk.jpg&h=4b313648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n她說可以有這麼大的差別，完全是因為瘦了下來加上化妝的緣故。她也貼出一張高三時的素顏照，完全可以看出已經變成美人了啊！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ntg3rWV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNtg3rWV.jpg&h=3f552b7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據她推特的資料，她身高只有144公分，但拍出來的照片實在很有個性，短髮也超級適合她啊。她現在則在新宿的酒吧RELUM擔任店長，不由得覺得她真的好厲害啊啊～<br />\n▼而且，可以這麼兇又這麼漂亮，到底是怎麼回事啦QQ<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/56s6pJD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F56s6pJD.jpg&h=5e7ebebe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3yyJrWY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3yyJrWY.jpg&h=9c8ac822&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/40383\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F40383&d=jj2gdENwcyF8UVQX%2BVtGpC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=c1c4eed3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/40383</a>"},{"pid":"56d1ede4331d56393945f176da827137840c8942","tid":954231,"uid":152701,"like":545,"dislike":48,"score":497,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:44:03.000Z","msg":"唔屌<br />\n完"},{"pid":"73d583fd1a3891dc861d3c5be0be077886403603","tid":954231,"uid":35699,"like":68,"dislike":37,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:44:21.000Z","msg":"本身靚d"},{"pid":"004c163e3c54c5eb77640cae929f5257ac361de7","tid":954231,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:44:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67869902ab66c3b5a253ee88da9c8783eb6fcf75","tid":954231,"uid":19454,"like":211,"dislike":0,"score":211,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:45:15.000Z","msg":"not素顏，乜樣都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e6312f461209fb019551e87a9de71673474eed","tid":954231,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff6d7c8e52c6cd9375c87eb106a4a871adb210b","tid":954231,"uid":126133,"like":158,"dislike":2,"score":156